reviewText: There is not enough of Cynthia singing......(And only one good interview when she was age 47)....but that was worth the price of this video....:-)

I thought the video would have more interviews with Cynthia.  Instead, there are interviews with other friends of the Gaithers.  I like the video but thought I was buying something with more about Cynthia.  Her singing is awesome but I was hoping to get to know more about her.
